Directory Kwic
==============

The directory contains tools to generate KWIC-Indices of ALDES-Modules.

Contents:
  SKIPWORDS:        File of words that may not be keys in a KWIC-index
  k2t.sed:          sed-script to transform an ALDES-KWIC-index to LaTeX-Format
  kwicdoc.tex:      LaTeX-frame for rk.tex (tabbing-environment)
  redux.kwic:       ALDES-KWIC-index for the ReDuX-system
                    (intermediate result of rkwic)
  rk.tex:           ALDES-KWIC-index for the ReDuX-System in LaTeX-Format
                    (result of rkwic)
  rkwic:            C-shell-script, that generates KWIC-Index in LaTeX-Format
                    for the ReDuX-system 
  wide10r.tex:      LaTeX page format
  xx.hd:            `header'-file of the module xx
                    (intermediate result of rkwic)
  xx.mhd:           `header'-Datei of the module xx in which eachline starts
                    with the module name ("xx ").b
                    (intermediate result of rkwic)
  kwic:             KWIC generator
  kwic.w:           nuweb source of kwic generator
  kwic.tex:         documentation of kwic (latex source, generated by nuweb)
  kwic.dvi:         documentation of kwic (dvi file, generated by nuweb)


To generate kwic call
% nuweb kwic.w
